videos.headline: Alabama gets it done on both sides of the ball
videos.description: Jarin Stevenson elevates for an impressive block, then Aden Holloway lays the rock in to pad the Crimson Tide's lead.

tracking.trackingName: NCB_One-Play (Alabama gets it done on both sides of the ball) 2024/11/05 ESHEET

videos.headline: Alabama's back-to-back buckets have the crowd on its feet
videos.description: Derrion Reid slams it home on the fast break, then Mark Sears nails a triple to pad the Crimson Tide's lead.

tracking.trackingName: NCB_One-Play (Alabama's back-to-back buckets have the crowd on its feet) 2024/11/05 ESHEET

videos.headline: Aden Holloway drains a 3 from the top of the key for Alabama
videos.description: Aden Holloawy gathers the rock and knocks down a 3 from the top of the key for the Crimson Tide.

tracking.trackingName: NCB_One-Play (Aden Holloway drains a 3 from the top of the key for Alabama) 2024/11/05 ESHEET

videos.headline: Fletcher Abee rises for a massive posterizing jam for UNC Asheville
videos.description: Fletcher Abee gathers the rock and slams down the hammer over his defender.

tracking.trackingName: NCB_One-Play (Fletcher Abee rises for a massive posterizing jam for UNC Asheville) 2024/11/05 ESHEET

videos.headline: Jarin Stevenson slams it home with authority for Alabama
videos.description: Jarin Stevenson gathers the dime and throws down the hammer to pad the Crimson Tide's lead.
